    "Great innovations deserve great stories",
    "Learn more about our associates",
    "We combine products with sensors, software and services and create cross-domain solutions from a single source for connected life. Create, code and develop the internet of things with us — from automated driving, via smart home, to industry 4.0: algorithm, data structure, machine learning, artificial intelligence, application and architecture for electronic systems.",
